Hello all... Again, the only reason Im posting is because Im at Clancy's and she is making me... ickenshlabin... haha, but she's fun. We watched like 10 minutes of A Clockwork Orange... It sucked I dont recommend it... no matter waht she says... DONT LISTEN TO HER!!! she's on a constant high... stoned eternally I tell you! hahah jk... dont do drugs...she doesnt do drugs either...yay for straight-edgedness... we're watching a movie at the moment, its about a little rat (a.k.a young child of feminine gender) and its riding on a pony (in a non-dirty way) and its funny, looking at her go... heehee... Clancy bought CDs not long ago... DOO WOP CDs ... Ugh, she made me listen to them, its horrible...they are horrible... ickenshlabin... hahahah... I dont feel like doing this anymore... I dont want to, you cant make me, I dont want to play! SO HA! hahah

                                          - Meggers

Well... haha, Chrissy is here... which is the only reason I'm posting... I hate this journal thing... its boring, its horrible... I like reading other people's... but not making one... meh... she's dancing with my dog... Its a chihuahua... Listening to muzak... HURRAH! school was cool.. HA! because it was my and the Chrissymister allll day... Hurrah.. we went to tims, to eat lunch... Yumm. It was gooood... Happiness is not a fish you can EAT! neeeuuuuuuup!!! she's serenading me...!!!!!! IN FRENCH... OOOH MA BLOOONDE OOOOOOH MA ROOOOOOUSSE!!! PETITIIIITTTEEE BLOOOOOOOONDDEEEE!  poof im out

hmm... well the past few days have been spiffy. Hung out with chrissy... did a little shopping a la spin-it... yeah. we watched movies and ate junk food... I hate this live journal thing.. HEAR THAT CHRISSY? you cant make me, I dont want to, I dont want to play...  gnuh gnuh... this is an utter bore fest. Oh, well I have a new suede poster! Yippy SKippy... Im leaving... I have more interesting things to do ... tourlou!

Well... This is my first post ever... Went to the beach today, I was kinda bored, but I brought the dog and my friend Chris, so it was allright.... sort of contradictory, but meh. The dog (Sofee, she's a chihuahua) went swimming, it was funny! When she came out she looked like a drowned rat.
   Anyways, the point of this post: Chrissy(AKA a_perfect_scar on LJ) came over! Woohoo! haha... Well... She called me to go for a walk,but I was too tired, she claims its laziness, but I keep telling her I was tired, the sun tires me. So she's here now. She started me with this LJ thing... It seemed cool... But.. yeah it seems cool. Later we are watching movies, 3 of them... which are:


 -Edward Scissorhands

 -Almost Famous
 
 -Zoolander

     So I guess thoses are the plans for the evening. We ate icecream earlier... isnt that rebelious, hehe... Anyways Im off...
